verbose_text: Quantitative analysis of mineralization by measuring the absorbance of Alizarin red S at 570 nm revealed a significant difference between the two groups on days 10 and 18 (P < 0.01; XREF_FIG), indicating that the knockdown of ANX A1 inhibited BM-MSC osteogenic differentiation.
evidence: ANX A1 inhibited BM-MSC osteogenic differentiation
